        "description": {
            "value": "<p>An understanding of how violence begets more violence fills your target, causing it mental anguish when it attempts to take violent actions. The target must attempt a Will saving throw.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The next time the target takes a hostile action, the target takes 1d4 mental damage; the spell's duration then ends.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The first time in a round when the target takes a hostile action, the target takes 1d4 mental damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Each time the target takes a hostile action, the target takes 1d4 mental damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The mental damage increases by 1d4.</p>"
